Analysis of PacMAN metabarcoding data

Saara Suominen, Pieter Provoost

This is a first analysis of the COI metabarcording data from PacMAN available as of July 2023. Raw sequence data have been analyzed with the PacMAN bioinformatics pipeline and the resulting Darwin Core tables are included in this repository.

The source for this notebook is hosted at https://github.com/iobis/pacman-data-analysis.
